---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken with Creamy Thyme Sauce, Mashed Sweet Potato, and Roasted Broccoli
description: After testing hundreds of recipes in the HelloFresh test kitchen, we’ve come up with a formula for the perfect recipe. Meat + sauce + potatoes + veggies! We know, it’s a groundbreaking discovery. This twist incorporates one of our favorite sauces, a creamy thyme sauce. It’s great on just about everything!
